Class FConvolution

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.image.processing.convolution.FConvolution
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CompassOperators.Compass0, CompassOperators.Compass135, CompassOperators.Compass45, CompassOperators.Compass90, Disk, FSobelX, FSobelY, Gaussian2D, Laplacian3x3, LaplacianOfGaussian2D

    public class FConvolution
extends Object
implements SinglebandImageProcessor<Float,FImage>
    Base class for implementation of classes that perform convolution operations on @link{FImage}s as a @link{SinglebandImageProcessor}, with the kernel itself formed from and @link{FImage}.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
